data.description: We have the title ready to finish a transaction to close, we have the lender that has the home nearly through underwriting, this home is ready for an "AS IS WHERE IS" conventional or cash closing as fast as your buyer can be approved!    Priced below auction of a similar layout home, and noting rehabbed prices for smaller homes in the area, this home is poised for profit boasting 400+ sf more than most homes and a 4 car garage just waiting for your hobbies!     Are You A Serious Investor or Handy Person looking for a solid home to make your own or do you like updating homes while you live in them?  THIS could be YOUR NEXT HOME with over 1900 SF of living space, and located directly across from the Catholic School.       The deck has multiple areas for entertaining, grilling, and relaxing after work.      Enter the sliding doors off of the back deck to the spacious kitchen and  adjoining dining area.  There is a gorgeous built in hutch between the two spaces. This area could become a master chef's dream with your touch and imagination!     There is gorgeous main floor woodwork throughout.  Do you like a cozy fireplace option? This home provides not one, but two fireplaces (unwarranted, not used by current owner) to make your own. One is a wood burner stove and one has gas hookup present. Entertaining is made easy with a wet bar area, an oversized entry and adjoining Living Room.      When you are ready to settle in for the night, the 3 bedrooms upstairs are conveniently located with the sprawling double vanity bathroom and a second-floor laundry in separate rooms for the ultimate convenience. Create an amazing spa and shower room, or get creative with a second bath option up here.      This isn't just a house; it's your next home, rental, or rehab.    #OhioHouse2Home #DreamHomeOpportunity #MiamiCountyHomes #PiquaHomes
